WEBVTT

00:02.160 --> 00:03.354
NARRATOR:
Previously on The Shield.

00:03.560 --> 00:06.438
CLAUDETTE:
Kleavon Gardner, questioned on
four separate homicides.

00:06.640 --> 00:09.598
Kleavon is not a killer.
I'm his sister. Believe me, I'd know it.

00:09.800 --> 00:10.915
We're releasing your brother.

00:11.120 --> 00:12.189
DUTCH:
Deep down, you know we're right.

00:12.400 --> 00:14.152
There's something wrong with him,
you just don't wanna see it.

00:14.360 --> 00:16.157
Now that you know,
things will add up.

00:16.360 --> 00:20.148
About six months ago, we found
this kilo of pure heroin in the
glove compartment your car.

00:20.360 --> 00:22.191
But you never logged it
into evidence.

00:22.400 --> 00:23.628
Lem got picked up by IAD.

00:23.840 --> 00:25.114
Got him wearing a wire.

00:25.360 --> 00:26.713
Kavanaugh might be planning
to formally arrest you.

00:26.920 --> 00:28.592
That happens, we'll be
ready to bail you out.

00:28.800 --> 00:29.755
You hired a lawyer?

00:29.960 --> 00:33.999
You need to shift perception,
make Internal Affairs look like
they're hurting good guys.

00:34.200 --> 00:37.078
I got Mackey making a deal with
the Russians. Hot prescription drugs.

00:37.280 --> 00:39.032
Here's our good faith.

00:39.240 --> 00:40.639
Yes.
COP: Do it.

00:40.840 --> 00:42.353
OFFICERS:
Freeze!

00:42.560 --> 00:44.915
[ALL SHOUTING]

00:46.520 --> 00:47.873
What the hell is going on?

00:48.080 --> 00:50.514
The IAD just shit all over our sting.
What's this?

00:50.720 --> 00:52.358
I don't know where you got
your intel, but it's wrong.

00:52.560 --> 00:54.278
He ran the whole operation
by me this afternoon.

00:54.480 --> 00:58.871
I guess IAD will spin any kind of
fiction to stain good cops bad.

01:01.080 --> 01:02.354
[TRUCK BEEPING]

01:02.560 --> 01:04.516
MAN:
Coming. Looks good, yeah.

01:08.000 --> 01:09.433
All right.

01:15.640 --> 01:17.676
