All right. Come on, down here, guys.

01:21.760 --> 01:24.911
BILLINGS:
Oh! Watch it.
Delicate machinery, people.

01:25.120 --> 01:27.076
MOVER: Oh, hang on.
BILLINGS: Careful, guys.

01:27.280 --> 01:29.236
Watch the turn. Watch the turn.

01:29.440 --> 01:31.112
Coming through. Heads up.

01:31.320 --> 01:32.389
DETECTIVE 1:
Heads up?

01:32.600 --> 01:33.999
DETECTIVE 2:
I'll grab it for evidentiary.

01:36.720 --> 01:38.676
BILLINGS:
Watch your back, Dutch boy.

01:42.400 --> 01:43.628
