02:00.240 --> 02:01.673
BILLINGS:
Careful. Come on.

02:03.000 --> 02:09.074
Learn the unknown English words
of this movie at www.skeebdo.com

02:10.479 --> 02:12.516
I give that couch two weeks
before we're moving it down here.

02:12.720 --> 02:13.948
I'm not wired.
You're what?

02:14.160 --> 02:15.991
Look. I'm not wired.
I don't get this guy.

02:16.200 --> 02:18.156
What did Kavanaugh say?
I can't find him.

02:18.360 --> 02:21.272
I went by the motel. It's empty.
I called his cell, offices, no answer.

02:21.480 --> 02:22.549
Why hasn't he arrested you?

02:22.760 --> 02:24.432
Maybe he never had a solid case.

02:24.640 --> 02:26.119
VIC:
You think he's packing it in?

02:26.320 --> 02:27.799
What, pull the plug on
the investigation?

02:28.000 --> 02:31.515
Until we're sure,
we act like it's still on.

02:31.720 --> 02:32.914
But I like the feeling I'm getting.

02:33.120 --> 02:34.109
[KNOCKS]

02:34.320 --> 02:37.471
Vic, I hate to start your morning
with this, but multiple gang homicide.

02:37.680 --> 02:41.389
Beautiful. Better than
a strong cup of coffee.

02:42.920 --> 02:44.990
[SIRENS WAILING]

02:47.840 --> 02:50.070
Set tripping?
JULIEN: Drive-by.

02:50.600 --> 02:53.353
Male victim's affiliated Bop Street
judging by the ink.

02:53.560 --> 02:55.312
It's what happens when
you cross enemy lines.

02:55.520 --> 02:58.512
SHANE:
That turf's been gang-neutral since
Antwon's crew slithered out of Dodge.

02:58.720 --> 03:01.598
Any witnesses?
Yeah. Friends of the deceased.

03:01.800 --> 03:03.552
And about as helpful.

03:03.880 --> 03:05.472
VIC:
Yo.

03:05.920 --> 03:07.239
You two see anything?

03:07.440 --> 03:08.873
Yeah, brothers having courage.

03:09.080 --> 03:12.072
My boys went down wet
like real G's.

03:12.280 --> 03:13.998
Do you know who did this?
KASPER: Some hater.

03:14.200 --> 03:17.670
They almost capped me and Moni too.
Beyond that I couldn't say.

03:17.880 --> 03:20.314
Did you get a look at the car?
We didn't see nothing.

03:20.520 --> 03:21.794
VIC:
Well, you better start
searching your memory

03:22.000 --> 03:24.992
or you're gonna get a good look
at the inside of our car
on the way to the station.

03:25.200 --> 03:28.749
So me and my breezie almost
catch hollow points and po-po
got his foot up my ass?

03:28.960 --> 03:31.315
