03:49.880 --> 03:51.393
Well, well, well.

03:51.600 --> 03:53.909
Pretty ballsy showing
your face around here.

03:54.120 --> 03:57.396
I get to officially notify you that
Internal Affairs is investigating

03:57.600 --> 03:59.716
all four members of your
former Strike Team.

03:59.920 --> 04:03.435
Well, you got burned trying
to make that case already.
Why don't you move on?

04:03.640 --> 04:06.791
Since all the Strike Team's files,
all your files on them are here,

04:07.000 --> 04:10.151
I'm gonna be setting up shop
in the Barn until my
investigation's complete.

04:10.360 --> 04:11.395
You're kidding me, right?

04:11.600 --> 04:12.794
[KAVANAUGH LAUGHING]

04:13.000 --> 04:15.468
Most of the time,
just not this time.

04:15.680 --> 04:18.831
Ahem. And where exactly do you
think you're gonna drop anchor?

04:19.040 --> 04:20.553
Well, I need some privacy,

04:20.760 --> 04:24.309
and I don't wanna restrict any
of these officers from using
the interrogation rooms.

04:24.520 --> 04:27.910
So the easiest thing for me
to do is to use your office.

04:30.000 --> 04:33.072
Excuse me, lieutenant. Are you
forgetting that I'm captain here?

04:33.280 --> 04:34.429
KAVANAUGH:
Acting captain.

04:34.680 --> 04:39.196
And that entitles you to a workspace
and a phone. Not a private office.

04:39.400 --> 04:44.679
But I understand the last captain
did very well right here on
the killing floor.

04:44.880 --> 04:47.075
Sorry for the inconvenience.

04:48.120 --> 04:49.473
Scott?

04:51.920 --> 04:53.478
Hey.

04:54.200 --> 04:55.792
Put that stuff...

04:56.000 --> 04:59.151
Put it over there till
I can work this shit out.

04:59.400 --> 05:01.470
I didn't see nothing.
I don't know nothing.

05:01.680 --> 05:04.717
I got nothing to say except thank
the Most High my man's okay.

05:04.920 --> 05:08.037
Your man? He's a kid and you're not.
How's that work?

05:08.240 --> 05:12.199
He laces me with nice shit
and got a big dick. It's all good.

05:12.400 --> 05:13.549
RONNIE:
You're a deep one.

05:13.760 --> 05:15.716
