05:22.920 --> 05:25.673
Arrogant little prick for
only being 19, Preston.

05:25.880 --> 05:29.077
That's my government name.
The homeys call me Kasper.

05:29.800 --> 05:31.472
The famous Kasper?

05:31.680 --> 05:34.433
Been making quite a name
for yourself these last
few months moving rock.

05:34.640 --> 05:36.596
You must have me confused
with some other cat.

05:36.800 --> 05:38.677
I hear you been working
with the rival sets.

05:38.880 --> 05:40.552
Black, brown, One-Niners,
Spookstreet.

05:40.760 --> 05:42.512
You're an equal-opportunity
dope dealer.

05:42.720 --> 05:44.119
Don't know about that.

05:44.320 --> 05:47.437
But see, when you white
in Farmington, you don't fit in,

05:47.640 --> 05:49.039
so you gotta make
friends everywhere.

05:49.240 --> 05:52.118
It'd make it a whole lot
easier on us if we just put
our heads together on this.

05:52.320 --> 05:56.029
Yeah, it would be. But see,
I ain't no cheese-eating rodent.

05:57.000 --> 05:58.877
VIC:
Looks like you been gnawing
on something nasty to me.

05:59.080 --> 06:00.069
[CELL PHONE RINGS]

06:01.160 --> 06:03.196
Yeah.
BILLINGS: Vic?

06:03.400 --> 06:04.719
We got issues here.

06:06.440 --> 06:08.396
What the hell
are you doing?

06:09.080 --> 06:11.548
KAVANAUGH:
I know this will come
as a big surprise to you,

06:11.760 --> 06:13.557
but you and your team

06:13.760 --> 06:15.876
are the subject of an
IAD investigation,

06:16.120 --> 06:17.235
which I am heading up.

06:17.440 --> 06:20.830
You already lost face in front of
the brass, blowing our Russian bust.

06:21.040 --> 06:24.237
How's this play helping you?
I appreciate your concern,

06:24.440 --> 06:26.396
but let me worry about that.

06:27.680 --> 06:30.717
Don't expect any cooperation
from those folks down there.

06:30.920 --> 06:32.273
They're a home crowd.

06:32.480 --> 06:34.550
I wouldn't do anything
to wanna upset them.

06:34.760 --> 06:38.036
Last thing I wanna do
is rock the boat.

06:42.680 --> 06:44.238
[###]

06:53.800 --> 06:54.949
Ahh.

06:55.160 --> 06:58.152
Man, if he'd arrest me already,
at least then he'd have to
lay out what he's got.

06:58.360 --> 06:59.315
[KNOCKS]

06:59.520 --> 07:01.431
Goddamn it.

07:02.840 --> 07:04.432
VIC:
Oh, come in.

07:05.400 --> 07:07.072
Hey.
BECCA: Hey.

07:07.280 --> 07:10.078
Lem, Ronnie, you
remember Becca Doyle
from the Crawford case.

07:10.280 --> 07:12.271
Yeah, hey.
VIC: Well, she's representing us now.

07:12.480 --> 07:14.835
Protecting us legally against
this nut job upstairs.

07:15.040 --> 07:16.314
You lawyered up?

07:16.520 --> 07:18.431
SHANE:
She's helping out all of us.

07:18.640 --> 07:20.995
For just such an occasion.
You're taken care of.

07:21.200 --> 07:23.191
Well, your boy Kavanaugh's
quite the loose cannon.

07:23.400 --> 07:25.994
Even his IAD buddies are
surprised by this move.

07:26.200 --> 07:30.193
He's made it personal, which
helps me make the case that
you're being unfairly targeted.

07:30.400 --> 07:31.549
[DOOR OPENS]

07:31.760 --> 07:36.356
Oh. This looks like
attorney-client privilege.

07:36.560 --> 07:37.595
Yes, it is.

07:38.120 --> 07:41.032
Ms. Doyle, is it?
Yes.

07:41.240 --> 07:42.992
Jon Kavanaugh.

07:43.200 --> 07:45.634
I'm representing all four
of these detectives.

07:45.840 --> 07:48.718
Make sure your communications
with them go through me.

07:48.920 --> 07:50.069
Oh, be my pleasure.

07:50.280 --> 07:53.636
Looking forward to working
with you. You just let me know
when you're ready, okay?

07:53.840 --> 07:55.512
All right.
Okay.

08:03.440 --> 08:05.351
All right. We gotta concentrate
on doing our jobs.

08:05.560 --> 08:08.154
Let her worry about whatever
bullshit charges he's trumping up.

08:08.360 --> 08:10.669
The last thing we want
is him getting at you
through some side door.

08:10.880 --> 08:13.838
Throws you off your game, he comes
at you on competency issues

08:14.040 --> 08:15.598
or some mistake you
make on the street.

08:15.800 --> 08:17.358
Well, we got some dead kids
to account for.

08:17.560 --> 08:19.949
Kasper and his squeeze gave us zip.
What's the next move?

08:20.160 --> 08:21.798
All right, the dead bangers
are Bop Street.

08:22.000 --> 08:25.356
It could be their own set
whacked them for breaking ranks,
working with white folks.

08:25.560 --> 08:27.516
That's a tree worth shaking.
LEM: All right.

08:27.720 --> 08:29.392
