legal right to let us inside.

11:13.480 --> 11:16.392
Kleavon been, uh,
keeping odd hours?

11:16.600 --> 11:18.511
Being secretive?

11:18.760 --> 11:21.672
FATIMA:
Nothing out of the ordinary,
except the shirt.

11:23.760 --> 11:25.830
His room's this way.

11:30.240 --> 11:32.800
All the furniture's mine.

11:36.800 --> 11:39.951
Only thing he brought
was, uh, the mirror.

11:41.480 --> 11:44.711
Kleavon do anything else
with his time besides work?

11:44.920 --> 11:48.754
Reads a little. Watches TV.
Like everyone else.

11:56.120 --> 11:57.838
Dear Lord.

11:58.240 --> 12:00.037
[DOOR CLOSES]
[FATIMA GASPS]

12:00.240 --> 12:01.992
Fatima?

12:02.240 --> 12:03.639
Fatima?

12:05.440 --> 12:06.634
[FATIMA GASPING]

12:06.840 --> 12:08.159
Fatima?

12:13.400 --> 12:16.073
FATIMA:
