Course.

12:29.720 --> 12:31.517
Come on, I'll make you some lunch.

12:40.080 --> 12:43.117
KLEAVON:
Can you believe all that time
and effort just to get across town

12:43.320 --> 12:44.878
then they send me
home after an hour?

12:45.080 --> 12:46.035
[FATIMA CHUCKLES]

12:46.240 --> 12:48.196
FATIMA: You want some pickles?
Sure.

12:48.400 --> 12:49.799
FATIMA:
