12:50.000 --> 12:53.709
What about that...? That other
job you were looking into?

12:53.920 --> 12:56.229
Oh, manager told me to
call back next week.

12:56.440 --> 12:57.714
FATIMA:
Oh, baby, something will turn up.

12:57.920 --> 13:00.718
KLEAVON:
Yeah. You going to
Barbara's house tonight?

13:02.760 --> 13:05.797
Just curious. Hey, you know,
we need some paper towels.

13:23.960 --> 13:26.474
Where the hell's our door?
The other one too.

13:26.960 --> 13:28.678
That son of a bitch.

13:28.880 --> 13:30.757
