13:33.960 --> 13:37.396
I assume you guys have got
nothing to hide, right?

13:37.640 --> 13:39.631
Anyway, with all the
confusion last week,

13:40.080 --> 13:44.358
I never did get a chance to
congratulate you on that bust.

13:44.560 --> 13:48.758
